/-!
# TrinityLean — Lean 4 Port of Trinity S³AI Structures

This package contains basic formalisations of the algebraic structures
underlying the Trinity S³AI framework:

* `TrinityLean.KODimension` — KO-dimension signs for real spectral triples
* `TrinityLean.QuaternionicLinearity` — quaternionic structure and norm theory
* `TrinityLean.Spectrum600Cell` — Dirac spectrum of the 600-cell
* `TrinityLean.EtaInvariant` — eta invariants for Platonic plumbing
* `TrinityLean.DiracOperator` — Dirac operators, gamma matrices, Clifford multiplication
* `TrinityLean.H4RootSystem` — H₄ Coxeter matrix and root-system scaffold (PR #11)
* `TrinityLean.Snub24Z3` — free Z₃ action and 3-partition of the snub 24-cell (PR #14)
* `TrinityLean.HamiltonFano` — Hamiltonian cycle of Q₃ encoding the Fano plane (PR #9)
-/
